                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Powell</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Port an Prince</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-03-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 22, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Powell reports that he has requested the Haitian Government for an extension
                    of time until May 18 for those Syrians who held false certificates of
                    naturalization, which request has been granted.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
